&lt;h3&gt;


Workflow Timeline
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Initial setup:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight shell"&gt;&lt;code&gt;1. npm &lt;span class="nb"&gt;install&lt;/span&gt;
‚îú‚îÄ Reads package.json
‚îú‚îÄ Resolves dependencies
‚îú‚îÄ Downloads packages
‚îú‚îÄ Builds node_modules/
‚îî‚îÄ Generates package-lock.json

2. npm run dev
‚îú‚îÄ npm looks up &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"dev"&lt;/span&gt; script &lt;span class="k"&gt;in &lt;/span&gt;package.json
‚îú‚îÄ Executes: vite &lt;span class="o"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;from node_modules/.bin/&lt;span class="o"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
‚îî‚îÄ Vite starts dev server
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Development cycle:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight shell"&gt;&lt;code&gt;1. Developer edits src/App.jsx

2. Vite&lt;span class="s1"&gt;'s file watcher detects change

3. Vite:
‚îú‚îÄ Invalidates module graph
‚îú‚îÄ Sends HMR payload via WebSocket
‚îî‚îÄ Waits for browser request

4. Browser:
‚îú‚îÄ Receives HMR update
‚îú‚îÄ Requests updated module
‚îî‚îÄ Vite transforms on-demand

5. React Fast Refresh:
‚îú‚îÄ Preserves component state
‚îî‚îÄ Re-renders changed component
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adding a new dependency:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight shell"&gt;&lt;code&gt;1. npm &lt;span class="nb"&gt;install &lt;/span&gt;lodash
‚îú‚îÄ Resolves version
‚îú‚îÄ Downloads package
‚îú‚îÄ Updates package.json
‚îú‚îÄ Updates package-lock.json
‚îî‚îÄ Adds to node_modules/

2. Vite detects new dependency
‚îî‚îÄ Pre-bundles lodash on next import

3. Import &lt;span class="k"&gt;in &lt;/span&gt;code:
import _ from &lt;span class="s1"&gt;'lodash'&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
‚îî‚îÄ Vite rewrites to: /@fs/.../lodash.js
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



