&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Vite is faster:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No re-bundling ‚Äî just re-transform one file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;esbuild transformation ‚Äî 10-100x faster than Babel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Precise module invalidation ‚Äî only changed module&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

